Subject: Tin screws / was Engine tin needed.


 I replace all of my screws with stainless steal allen head screws. They 
work great and look nice. And with ball-head allen wrenches you can get to 
pretty much all of the screws. These are most useful when bolting on the 
alt/gen. 

